{"documents":[{"title":"AUFS Visual Identity","typeoverride":null,"nopostershadow":null,"description":"In early 2018, I participated in - and won - a contest to entirely redesign AUFS' visual identity. This involved creating a distinct and recognizable brand for the society, through the creation of a new logo, color scheme, font guidelines, etc... which would be used across all social media channels and even within the films, as animated vanity cards.","contentblocks":[{"tag":null,"title":"Logo","stills":[{"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_aufs_metatag.jpg","hash":"thumbnail_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":245,"height":129,"size":4.53,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a.jpg"},"large":{"name":"large_aufs_metatag.jpg","hash":"large_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":1000,"height":525,"size":48.79,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a.jpg"},"medium":{"name":"medium_aufs_metatag.jpg","hash":"medium_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":750,"height":394,"size":28.49,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/medium_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a.jpg"},"small":{"name":"small_aufs_metatag.jpg","hash":"small_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":500,"height":263,"size":13.39,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/small_aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a.jpg"}},"url":"/uploads/aufs_metatag_8edc9e832a.jpg","caption":"","name":"aufs_metatag.jpg"},{"formats":{"thumbnail":{"name":"thumbnail_2aufs network flare2.jpg","hash":"thumbnail_2aufs_network_flare2_f75ea05a7d","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":245,"height":126,"size":3.91,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_2aufs_network_flare2_f75ea05a7d.jpg"},"large":{"name":"large_2aufs network flare2.jpg","hash":"large_2aufs_network_flare2_f75ea05a7d","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":1000,"height":514,"size":40.54,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_2aufs_network_flare2_f75ea05a7d.jpg"},"medi