"ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":1000,"height":514,"size":100.24,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_20years_stars6_b4b62bf141.jpg"},"medium":{"name":"medium_20years_stars6.jpg","hash":"medium_20years_stars6_b4b62bf141","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":750,"height":385,"size":57.32,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/medium_20years_stars6_b4b62bf141.jpg"},"small":{"name":"small_20years_stars6.jpg","hash":"small_20years_stars6_b4b62bf141","ext":".jpg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":500,"height":257,"size":24.45,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/small_20years_stars6_b4b62bf141.jpg"}},"url":"/uploads/20years_stars6_b4b62bf141.jpg","caption":"","name":"20years_stars6.jpg"}],"videoembed":null,"videoembedaspect":null,"beforeafters":[],"description":"The logo is a simple enough to be used in a wide variety of settings (such as posters, social media banners, facebook group banners, etc...) while remaining recognizable and distinct. A film camera is embedded over the top part to make it quickly recognisable as a filmmaking society, while the style is slightly reminiscent of stained glass, serving as an echo of the University's older buildings."},{"tag":null,"title":"Vanity card","stills":[],"videoembed":"https://youtu.be/dWMihE3ciIY","videoembedaspect":1.77,"beforeafters":[],"description":"I also worked on a few animated vanity cards, to be used at the beginning and end of AUFS projects. These were designed to be quick and fairly discrete, in order to easily adapt to the wide variety of films produced by AUFS, while still conveying the society's brand identity. The animation itself focuses on the recognizable long shadow, heavily featured in most of the logos and communications of the society."},{"tag":null,"title":null,"stills":[],"videoembed":null,"videoembedaspect":null,"beforeafters":[],"description":null}],"moreinfo":[],"date":"2018-02-15","id":"9","slug":"aufs-visual-identity","backgroundcolor":"#042633","foregroundcolor":"#ffffff","foregroundcolor2":"#ffffff","images":[{